{
  "sentences": [
    {
      "paraIndex": 0,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "周瑜请诸葛亮在三天内准备十万枝箭。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p1_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 1500
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 0,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "这个任务听起来很难，大家都替他担心。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p1_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 1500
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 0,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "诸葛亮却很从容，只说到时候一定交上。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p1_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 1500
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 0,
      "sentIndex": 3,
      "text": "他没有先解释很多，而是把需要的东西一件件记下来。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p1_s4.wav",
      "durationMs": 1500
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 1,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "他请鲁肃帮忙准备二十条草船，又在船上扎满草把。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p2_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 1500
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 1,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "鲁肃虽然不明白原因，还是按约定帮忙。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p2_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 1500
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 1,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "到了大雾很浓的清晨，江面白茫茫一片，远处几乎看不清。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p2_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 1500
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 2,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "诸葛亮让草船慢慢靠近曹营，又让船上敲起鼓声。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p3_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 1500
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 2,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "对岸的人看不清情况，只好向声音来的地方放出许多箭。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p3_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 1500
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 2,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "草船排得整整齐齐，像安静的朋友一起完成任务。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p3_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 1500
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 3,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "箭纷纷落在草把上，草船两边很快插满了箭。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p4_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 1500
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 3,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "诸葛亮看时机差不多，就带着船队顺风回来。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p4_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 1500
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 3,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "回来的路上，他还让船换个方向，好让两边都能装满。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p4_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 1500
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 4,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "三天期限到了，箭如数送到。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p5_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 1500
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 4,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "大家这才明白，诸葛亮靠的不是急躁，而是观察天气、准备周全和守住约定。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p5_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 1500
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 4,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "一个好办法，常常来自细心观察，也来自朋友之间的信任。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p5_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 1500
    }
  ]
}
